{"types":[{"section":"\n{{fr-adj}}\n\n# [[true]]\n#: {{uxi|fr|C'est '''vrai'''?|'''Really'''?}}\n#: {{ux|fr|Est-il '''vrai''' que vous ayez dit qu'il a besoin de notre aide ?|Is it true that you said he needs our help?\n}}\n#: {{ux|fr|Il est '''vrai''' que l'on a dit cela.|It is true that we said that.\n}}\n#: {{ux|fr|Il n'est pas '''vrai''' que l'on ait dit cela.|It is not true that we said that.\n}}\n# [[real]], [[proper]]\n#: {{syn|fr|réel|authentique}}\n#: {{ant|fr|faux}}\n# [[honest]], [[sincere]], [[truthful]]\n#: {{syn|fr|honnête|sincère}}\n#* '''2012''' (August 7), {{w|Manon Massé}}, quoted in: Judith Lussier, \"[https://urbania.ca/article/manon-masse-par-dela-la-moustache Manon Massé : par-delà la moustache],\" ''Urbania'':\n#*: {{quote|fr|On a attaché beaucoup d’importance à définir ce qu’est un '''vrai''' homme ou une '''vraie''' femme, j’ai hâte qu’on s’attarde à ce qu’est une femme '''vraie''' et un homme '''vrai'''.|So much importance has been placed on defining what makes someone a '''real''' man or a '''real''' woman; I'm looking forward to when we turn our attention to what makes a woman or a man '''true.'''}}\n\n","alt":[],"syn":["réel","authentique","honnête","sincère"],"type":"adj","forms":[{"g":"m","n":"s"}],"html":"<p><span class=\"headword-line\"><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"fr\">vrai</strong> (<i>feminine</i> <b class=\"Latn form-of lang-fr f|s-form-of\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/vraie#French\" title=\"vraie\">vraie</a></b>, <i>masculine plural</i> <b class=\"Latn form-of lang-fr m|p-form-of\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/vrais#French\" title=\"vrais\">vrais</a></b>, <i>feminine plural</i> <b class=\"Latn form-of lang-fr f|p-form-of\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/vraies#French\" title=\"vraies\">vraies</a></b>)</span>\n</p><ol><li><a href=\"/wiki/true\" title=\"true\">true</a>\n<dl><dd><span class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">C'est <b>vrai</b>?</i> ― <span class=\"e-translation\"><b>Really</b>?</span></span></dd>\n<dd><div class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Est-il <b>vrai</b> que vous ayez dit qu'il a besoin de notre aide ?</i><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\">Is it true that you said he needs our help?</span></dd></dl></div></dd>\n<dd><div class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Il est <b>vrai</b> que l'on a dit cela.</i><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\">It is true that we said that.</span></dd></dl></div></dd>\n<dd><div class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Il n'est pas <b>vrai</b> que l'on ait dit cela.</i><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\">It is not true that we said that.</span></dd></dl></div></dd></dl></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/real\" title=\"real\">real</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/proper\" title=\"proper\">proper</a>\n<dl><dd><span class=\"nyms synonym\"><span class=\"defdate\">Synonyms:</span> <span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/r%C3%A9el#French\" title=\"réel\">réel</a></span>, <span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/authentique#French\" title=\"authentique\">authentique</a></span></span></dd>\n<dd><span class=\"nyms antonym\"><span class=\"defdate\">Antonym:</span> <span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/faux#French\" title=\"faux\">faux</a></span></span></dd></dl></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/honest\" title=\"honest\">honest</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/sincere\" title=\"sincere\">sincere</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/truthful\" title=\"truthful\">truthful</a>\n<dl><dd><span class=\"nyms synonym\"><span class=\"defdate\">Synonyms:</span> <span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/honn%C3%AAte#French\" title=\"honnête\">honnête</a></span>, <span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"fr\"><a href=\"/wiki/sinc%C3%A8re#French\" title=\"sincère\">sincère</a></span></span></dd></dl>\n<ul><li><b>2012</b> (August 7), <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manon_Mass%C3%A9\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Manon Massé\">Manon Massé</a>, quoted in: Judith Lussier, \"<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://urbania.ca/article/manon-masse-par-dela-la-moustache\">Manon Massé&nbsp;: par-delà la moustache</a>,\" <i>Urbania</i>:\n<dl><dd><div class=\"h-quotation\"><span class=\"Latn e-quotation\" lang=\"fr\">On a attaché beaucoup d’importance à définir ce qu’est un <b>vrai</b> homme ou une <b>vraie</b> femme, j’ai hâte qu’on s’attarde à ce qu’est une femme <b>vraie</b> et un homme <b>vrai</b>.</span><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\">So much importance has been placed on defining what makes someone a <b>real</b> man or a <b>real</b> woman; I'm looking forward to when we turn our attention to what makes a woman or a man <b>true.</b></span></dd></dl></div></dd></dl></li></ul></li></ol>","trans":["true","real, proper","honest, sincere, truthful"]},{"section":"\n{{fr-adv}}\n\n# [[true]]; [[truly]]\n#: {{ux|fr|Raconter '''vrai'''|translation=to retell truly, without errors}}\n\n====Derived terms====\n{{col3|fr\n|à vrai dire\n|démêler le vrai du faux\n|montrer son vrai visage\n|plus vrai que nature\n|pour de vrai\n|se montrer sous son vrai jour\n|trop beau pour être vrai\n|vraiment\n|vraisemblable\n}}\n\n====Related terms====\n* {{l|fr|véracité}}\n* {{l|fr|véridique}}\n* {{l|fr|vérité}}\n\n","alt":[],"syn":[],"type":"adv","html":"<p><span class=\"headword-line\"><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"fr\">vrai</strong></span>\n</p><ol><li><a href=\"/wiki/true\" title=\"true\">true</a>; <a href=\"/wiki/truly\" title=\"truly\">truly</a>\n<dl><dd><div class=\"h-usage-example\"><i class=\"Latn mention e-example\" lang=\"fr\">Raconter <b>vrai</b></i><dl><dd><span class=\"e-translation\">to retell truly, without errors</span></dd></dl></div></dd></dl></li></ol><div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading4\"><h4 id=\"Derived_terms\">Derived terms</h4><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=vrai&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: D